586
00:39:51,389 --> 00:39:53,152
JOSEPH: Thank you
for saying so, Guatrau.

587
00:39:53,357 --> 00:39:55,723
There's a delicate matter
I need your help on.

588
00:39:56,894 --> 00:39:58,589
If I can,
you know I will.

589
00:39:59,430 --> 00:40:02,058
There is a man,
an important man,

590
00:40:02,733 --> 00:40:06,931
who has conveniently forgotten
how he got to be so important.

591
00:40:08,739 --> 00:40:11,765
