resolved in a civilized manner,

599
00:40:33,664 --> 00:40:37,327
and I can think of no other Tauron as
civilized as you, <i>Tse' Jospeh.</i>

600
00:40:40,538 --> 00:40:44,065
And who is this
I'm to negotiate with?

601
00:40:45,242 --> 00:40:47,904
Caprica's Minister
of Defense, Val Chambers.

602
00:40:52,183 --> 00:40:54,913
