to translate the data.

679
00:45:09,339 --> 00:45:11,398
But the information
being held in our heads

680
00:45:11,475 --> 00:45:14,171
is available
in other databases.

681
00:45:15,345 --> 00:45:18,610
People leave more than footprints
as they travel through life.

682
00:45:19,149 --> 00:45:22,585
Medical scans, DNA profiles,
psych evaluations,

683
00:45:22,653 --> 00:45:26,749
school records, e-mails,
recording videolaudio,

684
00:45:26,824 --> 00:45:28,348
CAT scans,
genetic typing,

685
00:45:28,425 --> 00:45:30,450
synaptic records,
security cameras,

686
00:45:30,527 --> 00:45:32,290
test results,
shopping records,

687
00:45:32,362 --> 00:45:34,330
talent shows, ball games,

688
00:45:34,398 --> 00:45:36,423
traffic tickets,
restaurant bills,

689
00:45:36,500 --> 00:45:38,297
phone records,
music lists,

690
00:45:38,368 --> 00:45:40,393
movie tickets, TV shows.

691
00:45:43,507 --> 00:45:45,839
