716
00:47:22,472 --> 00:47:25,168
to translate synaptic
records into usable data.

717
00:47:25,275 --> 00:47:26,401
She did.

718
00:47:26,476 --> 00:47:29,206
Yes, but a person
is much more than just

719
00:47:30,747 --> 00:47:32,510
a bunch of usable data.

720
00:47:33,517 --> 00:47:34,984
